\frac{4(n+1)^3}{4}=4(n+1)*\frac{(n+1)^2}{4}; 
\frac{n^2(n+1)^2}{4}+\frac{4(n+1)^3}{4}=n^2*\frac{(n+1)^2}{4}+4(n+1)*\frac{(n+1)^2}{4} =\frac{(n+1)^2}{4}*[n^2+4(n+1)],
