(n+1)^3
a\times(b+c)=(a\times b)+(a\times c).
a=\frac{(n+1)^2}{4},\qquad b=n^2,\qquad c=4(n+1).
\frac{(n+1)^2}{4}\times n^2=\frac{n^2(n+1)^2}{4},
\frac{(n+1)^2}{4}\times 4(n+1)=\frac{4(n+1)\times(n+1)^2}{4}=\frac{4(n+1)^3}{4}
